48
00:10:37.751 --> 00:10:39.294
Dengar sini, Jason hidup.

49
00:10:40.087 --> 00:10:42.672
Kami gali mayat dia.
Saya nak bakar mayat dia.


50
00:10:42.756 --> 00:10:44.966
Sekejap. Siapa nama awak?

51
00:10:45.133 --> 00:10:47.386
Tommy Jarvis tapi kita perlu buat sesuatu.

52
00:10:47.469 --> 00:10:49.971
