jalan kampung ini?


78
00:12:19.561 --> 00:12:20.854
Sekejap.

79
00:12:21.104 --> 00:12:23.315
Awak akui papan tanda sebut,
"Kem Forest Green"


80
00:12:23.398 --> 00:12:25.025
