199
00:20:53.116 --> 00:20:56.494
- Ini memang tak adil.
- Lagi-lagi tak adil.


200
00:20:56.577 --> 00:20:59.038
- Dengar sini, peperangan tak adil.
- Sudahlah.


201
00:20:59.122 --> 00:21:01.541
