274
00:27:26.467 --> 00:27:28.016
Ya!

275
00:27:28.302 --> 00:27:32.014
Okey. Ini hujung minggu
yang paling menyeronokkan?


276
00:27:32.306 --> 00:27:33.474
Ya!

277
00:27:33.557 --> 00:27:36.310
- Kita akan memancing?
- Ya!


278
00:27:36.394 --> 00:27:41.440
- Kita akan takutkan semua budak lelaki?
- Ya!


279
00:27:41.524 --> 00:27:43.818
Okey. Adakah kita akan…

280
00:27:45.694 --> 00:27:49.073
Kita takkan makan kubis Brussels?

281
00:27:49.156 --> 00:27:50.908
